ACT:
     Prevention of  Food Adulteration Act, 1954-Ss. 7(i), 11
(1) (b),  Prevention of	 Food Adulteration Rules, 1955-Rules
22 and	22-A-Sample taken  after  opening  sealed  container
having larger quantity than required-If valid.
     Prevention of  Food Adulteration  Act, 1954-Ss.  19 (2)
