     The Judgment of Court was delivered by
     VENKATARAMIAH. J. The above Criminal Appeals by Special
leave are filed against a common judgment delivered on April
24, 1980 by the High Court of Punjab and Haryana in Criminal
Misc. Nos.  196, 198,  1565, 1567,  1569, 1571 and 1573-M of
